### 3.6. SQL Schema (Supabase)

```sql
novels (id text PK, title, slug UNIQUE, created_at)
  └── scenes (id text PK, novel_id FK CASCADE, title, order_index CHECK ≥0, UNIQUE(novel_id, order_index))
        └── beats (id text PK, scene_id FK CASCADE, order_index, text, speaker, resonance_weights_json JSONB, hyper_prompts_json JSONB, UNIQUE(scene_id, order_index))
```

RLS: enabled, public read/write для `anon` і `authenticated` на всіх 3 таблицях.  
Індекси: `scenes_novel_id_order_idx`, `beats_scene_id_order_idx`.

